Interface Action

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CommandLineCondition, CommandLineInteraction, CommandLineVerification, Condition, EdifactFileCondition, EdifactFileInteraction, EdifactFileVerification, FileCondition, FileInteraction, FileVerification, FlatFileCondition, FlatFileInteraction, FlatFileVerification, GUICondition, GUIInteraction, GUIVerification, Interaction, SeparatedFileCondition, SeparatedFileInteraction, SeparatedFileVerification, Verification, WebGUICondition, WebGUIInteraction, WebGUIVerification
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Action
    Parent interface for all service actions which can provide file-based information useful for debugging.
    Author:
    Joerg Langnickel, Volker Bergmann
